snippet.title: The Factory Must Grow - Trailer
snippet.description:
Trailer for the video game, "The Factory Must Grow" created by Michael Pratt

About The Game:
The Factory Must Grow is a 3D first-person factory builder where you mine resources, craft machines, and research technology. Begin by unlocking your first technology, then expand into a sprawling, multi-layered production empire. From small setups to massive systems, your imagination is the only limit!

Available on Steam!

Credits:
 - Song
Seth_Makes_Sounds. "Crystal Castles". https://soundcloud.com/sethamakessounds/crystalcastles, 
15 January 2024,
